The evidence with the title 'Deepwater Horizon oil spill - Wikipedia ' says The Deepwater Horizon oil spill is an industrial disaster that began on april 20, 2010 , in the Gulf Of Mexico on the BP-operated Macondo Prospect. Killing eleven people , it is considered the largest marine oil spill in the history of the petroleum industry and estimated to be 8 % to 31% larger in volume than the previous largest  ... 
